data.title: Eurovision Song Contest 1964
data.text:
Copenhagen, Denmark

21st March

This is a chart of the Eurovision Song Contest 1964, which was held in Copengahen, in Tivoli Concert Hall. The presenter was Lotta Waever. The conductor was Kai Mortensen.

Here are the entries of 1964:
